{"tid":609979,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【講係咁講】中銀香港︰IT系統及客戶資料庫在港獨立運作","createTime":"2018-03-29T13:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T17:32:33.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a074cf8a985e74bdcfb586a71750bc1221695b9e","tid":609979,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:28:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1522329088287&amp;issue=20180329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1522329088287%26issue%3D20180329&d=fxjA2VzlHrE%2B8MrzBOvQPh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=12bd03c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1522329088287&amp;issue=20180329</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中銀香港（2388）將於本月31日晚上11時進行系統更新，網上有傳聞指，系統更新後客戶資料可能遺失，甚至有指是為了把客戶資料提交給中央。中銀香港副董事長兼總裁高迎欣表示，不認同上述說法，重申是次系統更新，是配合其區域性的發展。<br />\n<br />\n該行營運總監鍾向群強調，該行的IT系統及客戶資料庫都設在香港，且獨立運作，對客戶資料的處理，均嚴格遵守法律及私隱條例，因此呼籲客戶放心。<br />\n<br />\n記者：廖毅然<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacdb60f158af12b36e2105a17eea3ccfd1c43a0","tid":609979,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:29:17.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n當初間濕鳩公司一定要人個出糧戶口係中銀<br />\n好彩走左<br />\n唔係都唔點會轉左筆錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68db8c81aa6cd90d95cbd5d404a100a23477c58","tid":609979,"uid":49392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:30:30.000Z","msg":"中銀搞港獨"},{"pid":"63d9d2172c06dae4a6d86da2cdd521227dcf6adf","tid":609979,"uid":1886,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"IT系統及客戶資料庫在<span style=\"color: red;\">港獨</span>立運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44a9bb9435efcc61d7e9c4935c0cd4b018cd057","tid":609979,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201